nxuecity.com/news/2026/07/12/126705984.html?v=1783860494</link><description>&lt;div style="margin-bottom: 15px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://www.wenxuecity.com//adserver.wenxuecity.com/202512/1770925882861.png" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 6px; display: block;" /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-size: 14px; color: #444; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;"&gt;WENXUECITY.COM does not represent or guarantee the truthfulness, accuracy, or reliability of any of communications posted by other users. Copyright ©1998-2026wenxuecity.comAll rights reserved.Privacy ...&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.wenxuecity.com/news/2026/07/12/126705984.html?v=1783860494</guid><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 12:48:17 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>10万台“中国造”空调已发往欧洲</title><link>https://www.wenxuecity.com/news/2026/07/12/126705988.html?v=1783860494</link><description>&lt;div style="margin-bottom: 15px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://www.wenxuecity.com//adserver.wenxuecity.com/202512/1770925882861.png" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 6px; display: block;" /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-size: 14px; color: #444; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;"&gt;今年入夏以来，欧洲多国遭遇极端高温天气，法国、西班牙、德国等地气温持续逼近40摄氏度，多地接连发布高温红色预警。据广州日报7月11日报道，2026年4月至6月，国铁集团广州局通过中欧班列累计发运便携空调及核心配件货值约5200万美元，其中整机发运量突破10万台。一列列满载“中国造”便携空调的中欧班列从广州国际港等场站疾驰而出，跨越亚欧大陆，为欧洲民众送去阵阵凉风。与易受干扰、耗时漫长的海运相比，中...&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.wenxuecity.com/news/2026/07/12/126705988.html?v=1783860494</guid><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 12:48:15 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>